---
import '../../styles/home/final-cta.css';
---

<section class="py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20 px-4 bg-cover bg-center bg-no-repeat" style="background-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(34, 63, 43, 0.85), rgba(53, 100, 68, 0.75)), url('/images/earth.png');" data-reveal>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Empieza hoy a invertir con propósito</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-200 text-base md:text-lg mb-6 md:mb-8">Forma parte de una nueva generación de inversores que buscan impacto y crecimiento.</p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 md:gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="/login" class="px-6 md:px-8 py-3 rounded-full border border-white/30 bg-white/10 text-white font-semibold hover:bg-white/20 transition text-sm md:text-base">Crear cuenta</a>
      <a href="/planes" class="px-6 md:px-8 py-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-emerald-400 text-white font-bold hover:from-green-600 hover:to-emerald-500 transition text-sm md:text-base shadow-lg">Empezar a invertir</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
